Quest Information


Prequest:
Battle of the Sunbird

Given By: Arena Master

Giver Location: Grand Arena
This is a storyline quest.

Goals:
Defeat Ice Weavers and Collect 2 Spider Eyes
Talk to the Arena Master
Hand In: Arena Master
